      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "HARA'S MILLY (5) turned in a modest effort most recently when eighth at this track over 550m behind HOLLY'S BEAR (31.24) in a Grade 5. Was a winner prior to that. The form out of last race has been strong. Has claims if she runs up to expectations. HOLLY'S BEAR (3) was a brilliant winner two back but last start drifted back and wound up strongly to finish a 2.75 lengths third at this track (30.79). Although beaten ran one of the quickest times on the card last start. Hard to beat again. MISS BEAR (1) was in winning form two back (30.15) at Q Parklands but ran below best last time there, finishing 7th. The form from her last run is stacking up nicely. Has ability and is one of the better chances. WHITE MACK (6) is a last-start placegetter and ran good time - in the mix again.",
